{"tid":2106564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又有入境處人員中招","createTime":"2020-07-13T11:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T13:37:42.000Z","uid":6728,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef63fddf982d14744a90fd97a0d7c2664bc2c199","tid":2106564,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"灣仔入境事務大樓一名入境處人員確診<br />\n<br />\n入境處表示，一名在灣仔入境事務大樓14及16樓負責後勤工作的管制支援組男高級入境事務助理員，確診感染新型冠狀病毒。他最近沒有外遊紀錄，最近一次上班是上星期五，同日到診所求醫。他工作時一直有佩戴口罩，探測體溫正常，及遵守其他防疫措施。他工作的兩層樓並非公眾樓層，不對外開放，已即時安排全面清潔及消毒，包括所有公共設施。<br />\n<br />\n入境處指，衛生防護中心正嘗試了解他的感染原因，及有否密切接觸者。處方會積極配合，包括安排相關的入境處人員接受病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346874/灣仔入境事務大樓一名入境處人員確診\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346874%2F%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=3cb4403a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346874/灣仔入境事務大樓一名入境處人員確診</a>"},{"pid":"4fb0cb7df1471057a84b8c1538d3f73241ab75c5","tid":2106564,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"中招係基本法腐乳架"},{"pid":"8fe91e5d7368579dc9d604486caf56beea789d5c","tid":2106564,"uid":162906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f71603a2d4b08b4a38cbd5bf803508061be5fbe7","tid":2106564,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affd8dddf09d2c1e6a7fe97ab1a7dfa56ac427d4","tid":2106564,"uid":336429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef63fddf982d14744a90fd97a0d7c2664bc2c199","tid":2106564,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"灣仔入境事務大樓一名入境處人員確診<br />\n<br